{"old_string":"## Max line length

By default, the maximum line length is not set. The `android` code style sets the max line length to 100 (per Android Kotlin Style Guide).","file_path":"/project/documentation/snapshot/docs/rules/configuration-ktlint.md","new_string":"## Max line length

By default, the maximum line length is set to 140 (as defined in `ktlint_official` code style). The `android_studio` code style sets the max line length to 100 (per Android Kotlin Style Guide). For the `intellij_idea` code style the maximum line length is not set."}

{"old_string":"## Max line length

By default, the maximum line length is not set. The `android` code style sets the max line length to 100 (per Android Kotlin Style Guide).","new_string":"## Max line length

By default, the maximum line length is set to 140 (as defined in `ktlint_official` code style). The `android_studio` code style sets the max line length to 100 (per Android Kotlin Style Guide). For the `intellij_idea` code style the maximum line length is not set.","file_path":"/project/documentation/release-latest/docs/rules/configuration-ktlint.md"}

{"new_string":"    @Test
    fun `Given an empty EditorConfig and add a property with default value then the default value can be retrieved for the default code style`() {
        val editorConfig = EditorConfig().addPropertiesWithDefaultValueIfMissing(SOME_EDITOR_CONFIG_PROPERTY)

        val actual = editorConfig[SOME_EDITOR_CONFIG_PROPERTY]

        assertThat(actual).isEqualTo(SOME_PROPERTY_VALUE_OFFICIAL)
    }
","file_path":"/project/ktlint-rule-engine-core/src/test/kotlin/com/pinterest/ktlint/rule/engine/core/api/editorconfig/EditorConfigTest.kt","old_string":"    @Test
    fun `Given an empty EditorConfig and add a property with default value then the default value can be retrieved for the default code style`() {
        val editorConfig = EditorConfig().addPropertiesWithDefaultValueIfMissing(SOME_EDITOR_CONFIG_PROPERTY)

        val actual = editorConfig[SOME_EDITOR_CONFIG_PROPERTY]

        // Note that IntelliJ IDEA is the default code style for now, this will change to KTLINT_OFFICIAL in the future
        assertThat(actual).isEqualTo(SOME_PROPERTY_VALUE_INTELLIJ_IDEA)
    }
"}

{"file_path":"/project/ktlint-rule-engine-core/src/test/kotlin/com/pinterest/ktlint/rule/engine/core/api/editorconfig/EditorConfigTest.kt","old_string":"    @Test
    fun `Given an editorconfig containing a property for which the value is unset then return its default value`() {
        val editorConfig =
            EditorConfig(
                SOME_EDITOR_CONFIG_PROPERTY.toPropertyWithValue("unset"),
            )

        val actual = editorConfig[SOME_EDITOR_CONFIG_PROPERTY]

        assertThat(actual).isEqualTo(SOME_PROPERTY_VALUE_INTELLIJ_IDEA)
    }
","new_string":"    @Test
    fun `Given an editorconfig containing a property for which the value is unset then return its default value`() {
        val editorConfig =
            EditorConfig(
                SOME_EDITOR_CONFIG_PROPERTY.toPropertyWithValue("unset"),
            )

        val actual = editorConfig[SOME_EDITOR_CONFIG_PROPERTY]

        assertThat(actual).isEqualTo(SOME_PROPERTY_VALUE_OFFICIAL)
    }
"}

